>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"img-tab-1\">\n<p>    <figure style=\"width: 1035px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/dahahi.keymmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/link-dang-ky.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1035\" height=\"2090\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp qua link \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a DCheck<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section id=\"xuat-thiep-moi\">\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Xu\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi theo ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch<\/p>\n<p>    <figure style=\"width: 1035px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/dahahi.keymmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/JDI-2024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1035\" height=\"2090\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">DCheck t\u1ea3i file danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi do BTC g\u1eedi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n            <\/section>\n<section id=\"gui-thong-tin-xac-nhan-dang-ky\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>G\u1eedi th\u00f4ng tin x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c g\u1eedi:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Zalo (m\u1ea5t ph\u00ed): N\u1ed9i dung bao g\u1ed3m th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 m\u00e3 QR Code \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m<\/li>\n<li>Email: N\u1ed9i dung email bao g\u1ed3m th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, thi\u1ec7p m\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u00e3 QR Code \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"img-align\">\n<div class=\"img-tab-1\">\n            <figure style=\"width: 1035px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/dahahi.keymmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/ZNS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1035\" height=\"2090\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1eedi thi\u1ec7p ZNS<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n            <\/div>\n<div class=\"img-tab-1\">\n            <figure style=\"width: 1035px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/dahahi.keymmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mail-thu-moi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1035\" height=\"2090\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1eedi email<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n            <\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&#8211; \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin tham d\u1ef1<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt cho t\u1eebng kh\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/section>\n<section id=\"ho-tro-truoc-su-kien\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>\u2013 Theo nhu c\u1ea7u t\u1eebng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, DCheck l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi BTC v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m.<\/p>\n<p>\u2013 N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m theo nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a BTC (m\u1ea5t ph\u00ed v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3)<\/p>\n<\/section>\n<section id=\"trong-su-kien\" class=\"ht-title\">\n<h5><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right\"><\/i> Trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/h5>\n<\/section>\n<section id=\"checkin-face-qr\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>Checkin: Face\/QR Code t\u1eeb FaceID v\u00e0 app DCheck<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb FaceID:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Check in khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t<\/li>\n<li>Qu\u00e9t m\u00e3 QR Code<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"img-align\">\n<div class=\"img-tab-1\">\n         